             was indicted, for that <rs id="t17840707-24-off128" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840707-24-off128" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840707-24-off128" type="offenceSubcategory" value="fraud"></interp>
               he well knowing that one 
                     
                        <persName id="t17840707-24-victim304" type="victimName">
