               <p>Court to Shepherd. Did you see these parties execute it? - I did.</p>
               <p>Do you know the prisoner? - I cannot take upon myself to say I do, but the man<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178407070047"></xptr> who called himself 
               <persName id="t17840707-24-person324">
                  Thomas
