               <p>I am clerk to Mr. 
               <persName id="t17840707-24-person326">
                  Hooper
               <interp inst="t17840707-24-person326" type="given" value="Hooper"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840707-24-person326" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             the Navy agent, I know the prisoner, he applied to me on the 5th of January, in the name of 
               <persName id="t17840707-24-person327">
                  Thomas
                   Brady
               <interp inst="t17840707-24-person327" type="surname" value="Brady"></interp>
