             sworn.</p>
               <p>What ship did you serve on board? - The Pallas at sea, I remember the prisoner he went by the name of 
               <persName id="t17840707-24-person335">
                  Thomas
                   Brady
               <interp inst="t17840707-24-person335" type="surname" value="Brady"></interp>
