                  </persName>
            .</p>
               <p>Had he any brother on board that ship? - Not to my knowledge, I am sure that was the man that went by the name of 
               <persName id="t17840707-24-person337">
                  Thomas
                   Brady
               <interp inst="t17840707-24-person337" type="surname" value="Brady"></interp>
