               <p>I served on board the Pallas from the year 1781 to 1783, I remember the prisoner, I think he was on board when I went on board, he went by the name of 
               <persName id="t17840707-24-person339">
                  Thomas
                   Brady
               <interp inst="t17840707-24-person339" type="surname" value="Brady"></interp>
