               <p>Do you know the family of Power? - Yes, there were no other brothers but William, and John, and Michael.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17840707-24-person341">
                  MICHAEL
                   WARREN
               <interp inst="t17840707-24-person341" type="surname" value="WARREN"></interp>
